# Esskultur Cloudflare Platform — Development Notes

Last update: 2026-03-16

This document describes the **current development state of the Esskultur platform**.

The platform is designed as a **serverless restaurant operating system** built on Cloudflare.

---

# 1. Project Goal

Build a **Restaurant Operating Platform** supporting:

* multi-restaurant
* franchise model
* automated booking management
* ERP integration

Main components:

Cloudflare Workers → platform logic
Cloudflare D1 → source of truth
Odoo Online → ERP mirror
Staff mobile web app → operational interface

---

# 2. Core Architecture

Customer
↓
Website booking form
↓
Cloudflare Worker
↓
D1 database (source of truth)
↓
Staff mobile web app
↓
Odoo CRM / ERP mirror

Key rule:

Cloudflare D1 = MASTER
Odoo = MIRROR

---

