# 6. Stage System

Runtime stages:

pending
confirmed
arrived
done
cancelled
noshow

Mapping to Odoo:

pending → 1
confirmed → 2
arrived → 3
done → 4
cancelled → 5
noshow → 6

Cloudflare manages:

stage_runtime
stage_id

Odoo mirrors stage_id only.

---

# 7. Implemented APIs

List bookings:

GET /api/admin/bookings

Returns:

items[]

Important fields:

booking_time
contact_name
phone
x_studio_guests
x_studio_required_blocks
x_studio_stage_runtime
x_studio_source
updated_at

---

Change stage:

POST /api/admin/stage

Payload:

{
booking_id,
stage
}

Worker updates:

stage_runtime
stage_id
updated_at

and logs to:

booking_stage_log

